# 🔄 DevOps Lifecycle

The DevOps lifecycle represents the continuous process of delivering and improving software.

1. Planning
2. Development
3. Build
4. Testing
5. Release
6. Deployment
7. Operations
8. Monitoring

Each phase contributes to delivering value to customers quickly and reliably.

